title: Lana Jewelry Lion Necklace with Diamonds
description:
Inspired by Edward Kemeys's (American, 1843–1907) stately lion statues that adorn the museum entrance, our lion necklace will be the "mane" attraction of any outfit and exude undeniable confidence.  Made of 14-karat gold with diamonds. Designed by Chicago designer and founder of the luxe jewelry line Lana Jewelry, Lana Bramlette.   Go glam and channel  your inner celebrity!  

3/4 x 1/4 with 18 in. chain
